Class AbstractPlan

java.lang.Object
  mil.af.rl.jcat.plan.AbstractPlan

public final class AbstractPlan
extends Object
implements mil.af.rl.jcat.plan.PlanInterface

Title: AbstractPlan.java

Description: AbstractPlan is a logical representation of a plan. This implimentation of the plan also contains collaboration capabilities, where one plan serves as a server, and others act as observer clients.

Company: C3I
